const defaultState = {
	popUp: false,
	popUpMessageIndex : 0,
    messageArray : [],
    fetchError: false,
    fetching: false,
    fetchSuccess: false,
    postError: false,
    posting: false,
	postSuccess: false,
	stillNeedToFetch:true,
	doneFetchingAfterPost
};
export default defaultState;
